---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import DemoBlock from '../components/DemoBlock.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Free Alpine.js UI Patterns for Developers"
  description="Behavior-first Alpine.js patterns you can copy, adapt, and ship."
>
  <slot name="head">
    <script
      defer
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@alpinejs/focus@3.15/dist/cdn.min.js"
      integrity="sha256-6n4hVET1EQYZVJYhzQdgzt/ic/cIsUTU5lioe3AlVfk="
      crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </slot>

  <main id="main-content" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl space-y-8 px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="max-w-prose space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xl font-medium">
        Behavior-first Alpine.js patterns you can copy, adapt, and ship.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg/relaxed text-gray-700">
        HyperUX is not about repackaging HTML elements and functionality as components. It focuses
        on developer-friendly APIs for behavior-heavy UI patterns you can adapt to your own markup
        and styles.
      </p>

      <time datetime="2026-04-16" class="text-gray-500"> Last updated: 16 April 2026 </time>
    </article>

    <article class="space-y-4 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-300">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">How to Use These Experiments</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Each experiment includes live behavior and copy-ready output. Copy the HTML + JS, modify as
        needed for your project, and make it your own. Each copy button grabs the live demo markup
        and the related Alpine.js registration code.
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-gray-700">
        <li>
          <strong class="font-semibold">Tailwind CSS is scaffolding.</strong> The examples use Tailwind
          only for the demo — it will copy with the HTML, but feel free to strip it out and use your own
          styles.
        </li>

        <li>Keep accessibility and keyboard behavior intact.</li>

        <li>
          Customize the Alpine code — add features, remove what you don't need, adapt naming and
          structure to fit your codebase.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong class="font-semibold">Found a bug or improvement?</strong> Open an issue to share what
          you learned. Bugs we fix, useful patterns we consider for all experiments.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <hr class="h-px border-none bg-gray-300" />

      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong class="font-semibold">Ready to dive in?</strong> Use the navigation below to jump to a
        component demo and get copy-pasting.
      </p>

      <nav aria-label="Component navigation">
        <div
          x-data="huxDropdown({
            triggerId: 'component-nav',
            menuItems: [
              { label: 'Scroll Spy + TOC', href: '#component-scroll-spy' },
              { label: 'Combobox', href: '#component-combobox' },
              { label: 'Copy to Clipboard', href: '#component-copy' },
              { label: 'Dialog', href: '#component-dialog' },
              { label: 'Command Palette', href: '#component-command-palette' },
              { label: 'Dropdown', href: '#component-dropdown' },
              { label: 'Tabs', href: '#component-tabs' },
              { label: 'Resizable', href: '#component-resizable' }
            ]
          })"
          class="relative inline-block"
          x-on:click.outside="closeMenu()"
        >
          <button
            x-ref="dropdownTrigger"
            x-bind:id="triggerButtonId"
            type="button"
            x-bind:aria-expanded="isOpen.toString()"
            aria-haspopup="menu"
            x-bind:aria-controls="menuId"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-gray-100"
            x-on:click="toggleMenu()"
            x-on:keydown.down.prevent="openMenu(); focusFirstItem()"
            x-on:keydown.up.prevent="openMenu(); focusLastItem()"
            x-on:keydown.escape.prevent="closeMenu(true)"
            x-on:keydown.tab="if (isOpen) closeMenu()"
          >
            <span>Jump to component</span>

            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="size-4 transition-transform"
              x-bind:class="{ 'rotate-180': isOpen }"
            >
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </button>

          <div
            x-cloak
            x-show="isOpen"
            x-transition
            x-bind:id="menuId"
            role="menu"
            x-bind:aria-labelledby="triggerButtonId"
            class="absolute left-0 z-10 mt-2 min-w-48 overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-md"
            x-on:keydown.down.prevent="focusNextItem()"
            x-on:keydown.up.prevent="focusPreviousItem()"
            x-on:keydown.escape.stop.prevent="closeMenu(true)"
            x-on:keydown.home.prevent="focusFirstItem()"
            x-on:keydown.end.prevent="focusLastItem()"
            x-on:keydown.tab="closeMenu()"
          >
            <template x-for="(menuItem, menuIndex) in menuItems" x-bind:key="menuIndex">
              <div role="none">
                <template x-if="menuItem.href">
                  <a
                    x-bind:id="menuItemIds[menuIndex]"
                    x-bind:href="menuItem.href"
                    x-bind:tabindex="focusedIndex === menuIndex ? '0' : '-1'"
                    x-bind:class="{ 'bg-gray-100': focusedIndex === menuIndex }"
                    role="menuitem"
                    class="block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 focus:bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none"
                    x-on:click="selectItem(menuItem)"
                    x-on:mouseenter="focusedIndex = menuIndex"
                    x-on:focus="focusedIndex = menuIndex"
                    x-text="menuItem.label"></a>
                </template>

                <template x-if="!menuItem.href">
                  <button
                    x-bind:id="menuItemIds[menuIndex]"
                    type="button"
                    x-bind:tabindex="focusedIndex === menuIndex ? '0' : '-1'"
                    x-bind:class="{ 'bg-gray-100': focusedIndex === menuIndex }"
                    role="menuitem"
                    class="block w-full px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 focus:bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none"
                    x-on:click="selectItem(menuItem)"
                    x-on:mouseenter="focusedIndex = menuIndex"
                    x-on:focus="focusedIndex = menuIndex"
                    x-text="menuItem.label"></button>
                </template>
              </div>
            </template>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </article>

    <DemoBlock id="component-scroll-spy" title="Scroll Spy + TOC">
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        This example demonstrates a scroll spy component that tracks the visibility of heading
        elements within a scrollable container and updates the active state of corresponding items
        in a table of contents (TOC) navigation. The TOC allows users to click on items to smoothly
        scroll to the associated heading within the content area.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="font-semibold">Demo Config</strong>
      </p>

      <pre
        class="overflow-x-auto rounded-md bg-gray-800 p-4 text-sm text-gray-100">{`huxScrollSpy()`}</pre>

      <div
        x-data="huxScrollSpy"
        data-hux-copy="scrollSpyExample"
        class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div class="col-span-1 rounded-md bg-gray-50 p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Table of Contents</h3>

          <nav class="mt-2 space-y-2">
            <template x-for="headingItem in headingItems" x-bind:key="headingItem.id">
              <span
                class="block"
                x-bind:style="{ paddingLeft: (headingItem.level - 2) * 0.75 + 'rem' }"
              >
                <button
                  x-text="headingItem.text"
                  x-bind:class="{
                        'bg-blue-100 text-blue-900': activeHeadingId === headingItem.id,
                        'hover:bg-gray-100': activeHeadingId !== headingItem.id
                      }"
                  class="w-full rounded px-4 py-2 text-left transition-colors"
                  x-on:click="scrollToHeadingItem(headingItem.id)"></button>
              </span>
            </template>
          </nav>
        </div>

        <div x-ref="tocContent" class="max-h-128 space-y-4 overflow-y-auto p-4 md:col-span-2">
          <h2 id="getting-started" class="text-lg font-semibold">Getting Started</h2>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequatur nobis error minus
            vel quisquam qui ipsam velit nostrum nihil, ab itaque aperiam modi aspernatur asperiores
            dolor vero voluptate eius quasi et iste accusantium tempora minima! Hic neque sit a
            esse?
          </p>

          <h3 id="component-philosophy" class="font-semibold">Component Philosophy</h3>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Asperiores ut enim iure.
            Tenetur corrupti iste quibusdam, illo delectus libero nemo cupiditate sequi ex, odit eos
            dolor totam maiores porro quisquam!
          </p>

          <h4 id="copy-paste-contract" class="font-medium">Copy-Paste Contract</h4>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Pariatur quas aliquam labore
            tempore, perspiciatis dignissimos? Magnam numquam natus saepe aliquid.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Doloremque assumenda minima,
            id voluptatum nemo exercitationem!
          </p>

          <h2 id="accessibility-basics" class="text-lg font-semibold">Accessibility Basics</h2>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ab expedita quo quisquam,
            veritatis dignissimos placeat excepturi provident dicta eligendi ea voluptatibus neque
            ipsum consequuntur similique eveniet, animi, enim rerum dolor voluptatum itaque
            cupiditate! Iusto assumenda at voluptate corrupti voluptatum sed!
          </p>

          <h3 id="keyboard-support" class="font-semibold">Keyboard Support</h3>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi esse expedita aperiam
            quis veniam, iste repellat adipisci beatae. Voluptate reiciendis placeat eum sed harum
            ipsum, qui magni tenetur id accusantium.
          </p>

          <h4 id="focus-return" class="font-medium">Focus Return</h4>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quibusdam, quia quis
            praesentium nihil iusto quas officia fugit ut similique a!
          </p>

          <h2 id="authoring-patterns" class="text-lg font-semibold">Authoring Patterns</h2>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aperiam odit magnam expedita
            vitae! Vel, ratione. Error nostrum labore, cumque veritatis nemo quo at! Quo modi
            architecto, eligendi sint nesciunt illo obcaecati minima quasi odit, quod dolorem
            asperiores suscipit, animi dolor?
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Assumenda numquam doloribus
            fugit ullam tenetur natus vel? Quas quaerat tenetur consectetur distinctio cumque labore
            obcaecati dolorem dolores eius possimus. Aperiam tempore eligendi veritatis aut, illum,
            soluta asperiores quaerat autem quae ipsa non distinctio. Reiciendis corrupti dolorem
            quasi tempore, quibusdam quae quis, quo necessitatibus commodi voluptates quaerat? Qui
            velit officiis aliquam voluptate.
          </p>

          <h3 id="configuration-surface" class="font-semibold">Configuration Surface</h3>

          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi impedit deserunt illo
            assumenda corrupti consectetur nulla modi nobis architecto natus!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="font-semibold">All Options</p>

      <pre
        class="overflow-x-auto rounded-md bg-gray-800 p-4 text-sm text-gray-100">{`Options:
- headingSelector: string (default: 'h2, h3, h4, h5, h6')
- templateRef: string (default: 'tocContent')
- rootMargin: string (default: '0px 0px -60% 0px')
- visibilityThreshold: number | number[] (default: 0.1)`}</pre>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <button
          x-data="huxCopy({ sourceNames: ['scrollSpyExample', 'scrollSpyRegistrationCode'] })"
          class="rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-100"
          x-on:click="copyToClipboard()"
        >
          <span aria-live="polite" x-text="hasCopied ? 'Copied HTML + JS' : 'Copy HTML + JS'"
          ></span>
        </button>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/markmead/hyperux/issues/new"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
        >
          Found a bug or improvement? Open an issue.
        </a>
      </div>
    </DemoBlock>

    <DemoBlock id="component-combobox" title="Combobox">
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Searchable listbox input that follows the WAI-ARIA combobox pattern. Supports single or
        multiple selection, configurable template refs for input and listbox wiring, keyboard
        navigation, and outside-click close.
      </p>

      <strong class="block font-semibold">Demo Config</strong>

      <pre
        class="overflow-x-auto rounded-md bg-gray-800 p-4 text-sm text-gray-100">{`huxCombobox({
  optionItems: [
    { label: 'Apple', value: 'apple' },
    { label: 'Apricot', value: 'apricot' },
    { label: 'Banana', value: 'banana' },
    { label: 'Blueberry', value: 'blueberry' },
    { label: 'Cherry', value: 'cherry' },
    { label: 'Coconut', value: 'coconut' }
  ],
  clearSelectionOnInputClear: true
})`}</pre>

      <div
        x-data="huxCombobox({ optionItems: [{ label: 'Apple', value: 'apple' }, { label: 'Apricot', value: 'apricot' }, { label: 'Banana', value: 'banana' }, { label: 'Blueberry', value: 'blueberry' }, { label: 'Cherry', value: 'cherry' }, { label: 'Coconut', value: 'coconut' }], clearSelectionOnInputClear: true })"
        data-hux-copy="comboboxExample"
        class="space-y-2"
        x-on:click.outside="closeList()"
      >
        <label x-bind:for="comboboxInputId" class="block font-medium text-gray-700"> Fruit </label>

        <div class="relative">
          <input
            x-ref="comboboxInput"
            x-model="searchQuery"
            x-bind:id="comboboxInputId"
            x-bind:aria-expanded="isOpen.toString()"
            x-bind:aria-controls="listboxId"
            x-bind:aria-activedescendant="activeDescendantId"
            type="text"
            placeholder="Search fruits..."
            role="combobox"
            aria-autocomplete="list"
            aria-haspopup="listbox"
            autocomplete="off"
            class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none"
            x-on:focus="openList()"
            x-on:input="onInputChange()"
            x-on:keydown.down.prevent="focusNextOptionItem()"
            x-on:keydown.up.prevent="focusPreviousOptionItem()"
            x-on:keydown.enter.prevent="selectFocusedOptionItem()"
            x-on:keydown.escape.stop.prevent="closeList()"
            x-on:keydown.tab="closeList()"
          />

          <div
            x-cloak
            x-transition
            x-show="isOpen"
            x-ref="comboboxListbox"
            x-bind:id="listboxId"
            x-bind:aria-multiselectable="acceptMultiple ? 'true' : null"
            role="listbox"
            class="absolute z-10 mt-2 max-h-48 w-full overflow-y-auto rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white shadow-sm"
          >
            <template x-if="filteredOptionItems.length === 0">
              <p class="px-4 py-2 text-gray-500">No results.</p>
            </template>

            <template
              x-for="({ optionItem, sourceIndex }, optionIndex) in filteredOptionItems"
              x-bind:key="`${optionItem.value}-${sourceIndex}`"
            >
              <div
                x-bind:id="optionItemId(sourceIndex)"
                x-bind:aria-selected="isOptionSelected(optionItem).toString()"
                x-bind:class="{
                      'bg-blue-100 text-blue-900': focusedIndex === optionIndex,
                      'bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-900': isOptionSelected(optionItem) && focusedIndex !== optionIndex,
                      'bg-white': !isOptionSelected(optionItem) && focusedIndex !== optionIndex
                    }"
                role="option"
                class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between px-4 py-2"
                x-on:click="toggleOptionItem(optionItem)"
                x-on:mouseenter="focusedIndex = optionIndex"
              >
                <span x-text="optionItem.label"></span>

                <span x-cloak x-show="isOptionSelected(optionItem)" class="text-sm font-medium">
                  Selected
                </span>
              </div>
            </template>
          </div>
        </div>

        <template x-if="acceptMultiple">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <template
              x-for="(selectedItem, selectedIndex) in selectedValues"
              x-bind:key="`${selectedItem}-${selectedIndex}`"
            >
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-2 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-900"
              >
                <span x-text="getLabelForValue(selectedItem)"></span>

                <button
                  type="button"
                  class="inline-flex size-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-200/80 text-emerald-900 hover:bg-emerald-300"
                  x-bind:aria-label="`Remove ${getLabelForValue(selectedItem)}`"
                  x-on:click.stop="removeSelectedOptionItem(selectedItem)"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    class="size-5"
                  >
                    <path
                      d="M6.28 5.22a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 1 0 1.06 1.06L10 11.06l3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 1 0 1.06-1.06L11.06 10l3.72-3.72a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 6.28 5.22Z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </button>
              </span>
            </template>
          </div>
        </template>

        <template x-if="!acceptMultiple">
          <div
            x-cloak
            x-show="selectedValue"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-2 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-900"
          >
            <span x-text="getLabelForValue(selectedValue)"></span>

            <button
              type="button"
              class="inline-flex size-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-200/80 text-emerald-900 hover:bg-emerald-300"
              aria-label="Clear selected value"
              x-on:click.stop="clearSelection()"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="size-5"
              >
                <path
                  d="M6.28 5.22a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 1 0 1.06 1.06L10 11.06l3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 1 0 1.06-1.06L11.06 10l3.72-3.72a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 6.28 5.22Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </template>
      </div>

      <p class="font-semibold">All Options</p>

      <pre
        class="overflow-x-auto rounded-md bg-gray-800 p-4 text-sm text-gray-100">{`Options:
- optionItems: {label: string, value: string}[] (default: [])
- acceptMultiple: boolean (default: false)
- clearSelectionOnInputClear: boolean (default: false)
- hideOptionItemsWhenSearchQueryEmpty: boolean (default: false)
- inputTemplateRef: string (default: 'comboboxInput')
- listboxTemplateRef: string (default: 'comboboxListbox')`}</pre>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <button
          x-data="huxCopy({ sourceNames: ['comboboxExample', 'comboboxRegistrationCode'] })"
          class="rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-100"
          x-on:click="copyToClipboard()"
        >
          <span aria-live="polite" x-text="hasCopied ? 'Copied HTML + JS' : 'Copy HTML + JS'"
          ></span>
        </button>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/markmead/hyperux/issues/new"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
        >
          Found a bug or improvement? Open an issue.
        </a>
      </div>
    </DemoBlock>

    <DemoBlock id="component-copy" title="Copy to Clipboard">
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Utility component that copies multiple markup and value sources from live DOM elements by
        their data-hux-copy identifier. It preserves array order and joins sources using
        contentSeparator.
      </p>

      <strong class="block font-semibold">Demo Config</strong>

      <pre
        class="overflow-x-auto rounded-md bg-gray-800 p-4 text-sm text-gray-100">{`huxCopy({
  sourceNames: ['copyExample', 'copyRegistrationCode']
})`}</pre>

      <div class="space-y-4 rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">
        <div data-hux-copy="copyExample" class="space-y-4">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div
              class="space-y-4 rounded-md border border-dashed border-gray-200 bg-white p-4"
              data-hux-copy="copyExampleA"
            >
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-teal-300 bg-teal-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-teal-900 uppercase"
              >
                Element A
              </span>

              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Error quaerat obcaecati
                hic exercitationem? Libero unde dolorem est nostrum qui distinctio cum modi minima
                laudantium quia. Itaque consectetur totam adipisci magnam?
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="space-y-4 rounded-md border border-dashed border-gray-200 bg-white p-4"
              data-hux-copy="copyExampleB"
            >
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-teal-300 bg-teal-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-teal-900 uppercase"
              >
                Element B
              </span>

              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Possimus praesentium quasi
                aliquid molestiae at accusantium veritatis, minima dicta sed voluptatem.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button
            x-data="huxCopy({ sourceNames: ['copyExampleA', 'copyExampleB'] })"
            class="rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-100"
            x-on:click="copyToClipboard()"
          >
            <span aria-live="polite" x-text="hasCopied ? 'Copied' : 'Copy'"></span>
          </button>

          <div>
            <label for="hux-copy-input-demo" class="block font-medium text-gray-700">
              Input Value
            </label>

            <div class="relative mt-2">
              <input
                id="hux-copy-input-demo"
                data-hux-copy="copyInputExample"
                type="text"
                value="Hello there 👋"
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white py-2 pr-12 pl-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none"
              />

              <button
                type="button"
                x-data="huxCopy({ valueSourceNames: ['copyInputExample'] })"
                aria-label="Copy input value"
                class="absolute top-1.25 right-1.25 grid size-8 place-content-center rounded text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-gray-100"
                x-bind:class="{ 'bg-gray-100': hasCopied }"
                x-on:click="copyToClipboard()"
              >
                <span
